itter}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Holden-Ried, Kris}}\n[[Category:1973 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Canadian male film actors]]\n[[Category:Canadian male television actors]]\n[[Category:People from Pickering, Ontario]]\n[[Category:20th-century Canadian male actors]]\n[[Category:21st-century Canadian male actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Ontario]]\n", "name_user": "Gladmax", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eFilmography:Wikified The Crossing to The Crossing (2000 film)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kris_Holden-Ried"}
