ile}} [[1941 South American Championship|1941]]\n|Third place||3rd||4||2||0||2||6||3\n|- \n|{{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1942 South American Championship|1942]]\n|Sixth place||6th||6||1||1||4||4||15\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#c96;\"\n|style=\"border:3px solid red\"|{{flagicon|Chile}} [[1945 South American Championship|1945]]\n|Third place||3rd||6||4||1||1||15||5\n|- \n|{{flagicon|Argentina|alt}} [[1946 South American Championship|1946]]\n|Fifth place||5th||5||2||0||3||8||11\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:LemonChiffon;\"\n|{{flagicon|Ecuador|1900}} [[1947 South American Championship|1947]]\n|Fourth place||4th||7||4||1||2||14||13\n|- \n|{{flagicon|Brazil}} [[1949 South American Championship|1949]]\n|Fifth place||5th||7||2||1||4||10||14\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:LemonChiffon;\"\n|{{flagicon|Peru}} [[1953 South American Championship|1953]]\n|Fourth place||4th||6||3||1||2||10||10\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:silver;\"\n|style=\"border:3px solid red\"|{{flagicon|Chile}} [[1955 South American Championship|1955]]\n|'''Runners-up'''||'''2nd'''||'''5'''||'''3'''||'''1'''||'''1'''||'''19'''||'''8'''\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:silver;\"\n|{{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1956 South American Championship|1956]]\n|'''Runners-up'''||'''2nd'''||'''5'''||'''3'''||'''0'''||'''2'''||'''11'''||'''8'''\n|- \n|{{flagicon|Peru}} [[1957 South American Championship|1957]]\n|Sixth place||6th||6||1||1||4||9||17\n|- \n|{{flagicon|Argentina|alt}} [[1959 South American Championship (Argentina)|1959]]\n|Fifth place||5th||6||2||1||3||9||14\n|- \n|{{flagicon|Ecuador|1900}} [[1959 South American Championship (Ecuador)|1959]]\n|colspan=8 rowspan=2|''Did not participate''\n|- \n|{{flagicon|Bolivia}} [[1963 South American Championship|1963]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background:#c96;\"\n|{{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1967 South American Championship|1967]]\n|Third place||3rd||5||2||2||1||8||6\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|{{flagicon|South Americ