e=\"background:mediumblue; color:red;\"| Position\n|-\n| {{flagicon|PAK}} [[Salman Iqbal]] (ARY Group)\n| Owner\n|-\n| {{flagicon|PAK}} Tariq Wasi\n| CEO\n|-\n| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Dean Jones (cricketer)|Dean Jones]]\n| Head coach \n|-\n|-\n| {{flagicon|PAK}} [[Wasim Akram]]\n| Bowling Mentor & President<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://pakistansuperleaguepsl.com/psl-4-wasim-akram-joins-karachi-kings-as-president/|title=PSL 4: Wasim Akram Joins Karachi Kings as President|date=2018-11-14|work=Live Cricket Streaming Online|access-date=2018-11-14|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagicon|PAK}} [[Faisal Iqbal]]\n| Batting coach\n|-\n|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Johan Botha (cricketer)|Johan Botha]]\n|Assistant Coach\n|-\n|{{flagicon|PAK}} Faisal Mirza\n|Media manager<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.baaghitv.com/faisal-mirza-takes-over-as-new-media-manager-of-karachi-kings/|title=Faisal Mirza takes over as new Media Manager of Karachi Kings|author=Mehreen Saqib|work=baaghi Tv|date=29 January 2020|accessdate=16 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagicon|PAK}} Ibrahim Qureshi\n| Fitness trainer\n|-\n|}\n\n==Captains==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:100%\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | No.\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red;\"| Nat.\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | Player\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | From\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | To\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | {{Tooltip|Mat|No. of Matches as Captain}}\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | {{Tooltip|Won|Won}}\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | {{Tooltip|Lost|Lost}}\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | {{Tooltip|Tie&W|Tied}}\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | {{Tooltip|Tie&L|Tied}}\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | {{Tooltip|NR|No Result}}\n! style=\"background:mediumblue; color:red\" | {{Tooltip|%|Win Percentage}}\n|-\n| 1\n| {{flagicon|PAK}}\n| [[Shoaib Malik]]\n| 2016