r players who play enough games during the year can also gain Incremental contracts.\n\n'''Key'''\n*S/N = Shirt number\n*C/T = Contract type (Test / White-ball / Incremental)\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" \n|-\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Name\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Age\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Batting style\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Bowling style\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Domestic team\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| C/T<ref>{{Cite web |title=ECB announces Men's Central Contracts for the 2019/20 season |url=https://www.ecb.co.uk/england/men/news/1349647/-ecb-announces-men-s-central-contracts-for-the-2019-20-season |website=ecb.co.uk |publisher=England & Wales Cricket Board |date=20 September 2019 |access-date=20 September 2019 }}</ref>\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Forms<!--NOTE: This refers to the forms they've played for England in the past year, not over their whole England career-->\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| S/N<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/england/content/story/209588.html |title=ESPN Cricinfo \u2013 England ODI/Twenty Shirt Numbers |publisher=ESPNcricinfo |accessdate=1 August 2013 |date=18 May 2005 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601075617/http://www.espncricinfo.com/england/content/story/209588.html |archive-date=1 June 2013 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Captaincy\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Last Test\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Last ODI\n!style=\"text-align:center;background:skyblue;color:#000060\"| Last T20I\n|-\n!colspan=\"12\"| Batsmen\n|-\n| [[Tom Banton]] || {{age|1998|11|11}} || Right-handed || \u2013 ||